Package com.flag4j.core

Interface TensorOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X extends Number>

Type Parameters:
T - Tensor type.
U - Dense Tensor type.
V - Sparse Tensor type.
W - Complex Tensor type.
Y - Real Tensor type.
X - Tensor entry type.
All Known Subinterfaces:
ComplexMatrixMixin<T,​Y>, MatrixOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X>, RealMatrixMixin<T,​W>, VectorOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X,​TT,​UU,​VV,​WW>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Matrix
interface TensorOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X extends Number>
This interface specifies operations which all tensors (i.e. matrices and vectors) should implement.

      T sqrt()
      Computes the element-wise square root of a tensor.
      Returns:
      The result of applying an element-wise square root to this tensor. Note, this method will compute the principle square root i.e. the square root with positive real part.

    • abs
